  "text": "We performed Gene Set Enrichment Analysis (GSEA) between high-risk and low-risk group as separated by the 7-IRG signature via clusterProfiler and enrichplot R package. Two functions (gseGO and gseKEGG) were applied to identify the enriched terms in Gene Ontology (GO) and KEGG with a false discovery rate (FDR) value < 0.05 [CITATION_1] .",
